products.title: Graduation 2007 Takashi Murakami Euro Hat
products.content:
Authentic Item.
Graduation 2007 Takashi Murakami Euro Hat. One of the rarest items from the Graduation/Glow In The Dark Tour Era. This hat is a trucker hat featuring an amazing embroidery work of the Takashi Murakami bear. The bear has actual fur stitched on as well & the brim of the hat is thick and padded.

products.title: JIK 2019 Sunday Service Detroit Long Sleeve
products.content:
Authentic Item.
IK 2019 Sunday Service Detroit Long Sleeve. During the JIK Era, Sunday Service played an important role, leading into the album. Almost like a new version of GOOD Friday’s. This design is on a mock neck, displaying a front design of Sunday Service.
Measurements (Inches): Medium 22 Width 25 Length. XLarge 25 Width, 29 Length.
